lead_paragraph: Leicester's adventures in Premier League wonderland continued on Saturday as Jamie Vardy rediscovered his goalscoring touch in a deserved victory over Stoke that thrust them to the top of the table.

headline.print_headline: Vardy on Target Again as Leicester Fairytale Continues
